uot;https://www.theverge.com/24262440/amazon-prime-day-best-cheap-tech- Deals-under-50-october-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24262440/amazon-prime-day-best-cheap-tech-deals-under-50-october-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24262440/amazon-prime-day-best-cheap-tech-deals-under-50-october-2024</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-08T11:50:09-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-08T11:50:09-04:00</updated><title> Prime Day AirPods Pro 2 价格比以往任何时候都低至 169 美元</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;AirPods Pro 2022 型号坐在橙色底座上。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/6L9e1JNbxhIi7jOJUqsNRPl7jyA=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73639692/226285_AIRPODS_PRO_2_cwelch_ 0011.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;第二代 AirPods Pro 提供了 Apple 耳塞系列中最完整的套件，而且它们只会随着时间的推移而不断改进。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;ONErOb&quot;>;亚马逊的第二个 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24255302/amazon-prime-day-deals- Tips-news-guide-2024-october&quot;>;年度黄金日&lt;/a>;即将到来 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/24262468/amazon-prime-day-best -deals-sales-tech-gadgets-october-2024&quot;>;全面节省成本&lt;/a>;，但有些优惠确实脱颖而出。以&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23365910/apple-airpods-pro-第二代-review&quot;>;&lt;strong>;AirPods Pro 2&lt;/strong>;&lt;/a>;为例 -配有 USB-C 充电盒的一对具有 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0D1XD1ZV3?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;spoken nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>; Prime 会员的价格一路暴跌至 168.99 美元&lt;/a>;（约合 81 美元），追平历史最低点。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;nWamis&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Apple 的 AirPods Pro 变得更好了——无论外壳上有哪个端口&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23878402/apple-airpods- pro-usb-c-adaptive-audio-conversation-awareness-test-review&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;您可以使用这些智能保护套轻松将所有 Apple AirPods 升级到 USB-C &quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/2024/10/3/24260280/apple-airpods-pro-max-usb-c-upgrade-ken-pillonel&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;这是您最优惠的 AirPods 优惠现在就可以获取 &quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21302051/best-apple-airpods-deals&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;D5SZfv&quot;>;值得注意的是，该价格比最近发布的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DGJ7HYG1?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; 便宜约 10 美元target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;售价 179 美元的 AirPods 4&lt;/a>;，也具有主动降噪功能。尽管 AirPods 4 是较新的产品，但 AirPods Pro 为您提供了更多功能，而且物有所值，因此显然现在购买更划算。&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;1gBugu&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot; Productcard:12375646&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;pC0MxX&quot;>;事实上，如果您需要 ANC，您绝对应该选择第二代 AirPods Pro。虽然我们&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24245570/apple-airpods-4-review&quot;>;在我们的评测中发现 AirPods 4 的 ANC 非常有效&lt;/a>;，但您应该... &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265115/apple-airpods-pro-amazon-prime-day-deal-sale-october&quot;>;继续阅读……&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265115/apple-airpods-pro-amazon-prime-day-deal-sale-october" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265115/apple-airpods-pro-amazon-prime-day-deal-sale-october</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-08T11:45:55-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-08T11:45:55-04:00</updated><title> TikTok 因涉嫌伤害青少年而受到十几起州诉讼</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;黑色背景上的 TikTok 名称徽标，带有重复的粉红色和水绿色徽标&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/bfWofgQ4jhZOi-HIi_HnjGYX8qk=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873 /cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73639684/STK051_VRG_Illo_N_Barclay_9_tiktok.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;尼克·巴克莱 / The Verge 的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;JRhf20&quot; >;来自 14 个州和地区的总检察长&lt;a href=&quot;https://ag.ny.gov/press-release/2024/attorney-general-james-sues-tiktok-harming-childrens-mental-health&quot;>;起诉 TikTok涉嫌损害儿童心理健康&lt;/a>;并误导公众了解其平台的安全性。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;QbwVRC&quot;>;由纽约州议员利蒂西亚·詹姆斯 (Letitia James) 和加利福尼亚州议员罗布·邦塔 (Rob Bonta) 领导的两党 AG 小组，每个人都提起诉讼，指控其违反自己州的法律。邦塔在一份声明中表示：“我们的调查显示，TikTok 培养社交媒体成瘾是为了提高企业利润。” “TikTok 故意针对儿童，因为他们知道孩子们还没有防御能力或能力来围绕令人上瘾的内容建立健康的界限。”詹姆斯称这些诉讼是“保护年轻人并帮助应对全国范围内的青少年心理健康危机”努力的一部分。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;VqBbJU&quot;>;这些诉讼......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265169/tiktok-lawsuit-state-attorneys-general-kids-mental-health&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265169/tiktok-lawsuit-state-attorneys-general-kids-mental-health" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265169/tiktok-lawsuit-state-attorneys-general-kids-mental-health</id><author><name>劳伦·费纳</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-08T11:17:23-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-08T11:17:23-04:00</updated><title>兴登堡研究公司 (Hindenburg Research) 指控 Roblox 在用户数量上向投资者撒谎</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Roblox 的屏幕截图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/MZVZ0uoDbTZRMKf3BzWyYpHAoH0=/150x0:1770x1080/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image /image/73639644/roblox_screenshot.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Roblox&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;3k5r5n&quot;>;Roblox 面临指控，称其向投资者谎报了参与该项目的人数使用该平台。在周二发布的一份报告中，&lt;a href=&quot;https://hindenburgresearch.com/roblox/&quot;>;投资公司 Hindenburg Research&lt;/a>; 声称 Roblox“始终将其平台上的人数夸大了 25%， 42% 或更多。”&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;edwRHg&quot;>;Roblox，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2020/11/19/21578491/roblox-ipo-announced-dau -increase-pandemic&quot;>;于 2021 年上市&lt;/a>;，据报道 &lt;a hre